gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 116, Rockets 86
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Rockets, 116-86. Cole Anthony led the way with 20 points and eight rebounds for the Magic, while Franz Wagner added 17 points and three 3pt. FG in the victory. Dillon Brooks (four rebounds) and Fred VanVleet (five assists) tallied 14 points each for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Magic improve to 1-0 on the season, while the Rockets fall to 0-1.
